RT @centrifuge: Say hello to the first RWA lending market on @base using the @MorphoLabs Protocol.

@SteakhouseFi and @Re7Capital will curate the Morpho Vaults which include collateral from @centrifuge, @MidasRWA, and @Hashnote_Labs.

This is the first institutional grade lending market integrated with @Coinbase Verifications, allowing investors to streamline their onboarding process seamlessly through a single click.

Collateralize and borrow against:
‚Ä¢ @anemoycapital's Liquid Treasury Fund (LTF)
‚Ä¢ @MidasRWA's Short-Term US Treasuries (mTBILL)
‚Ä¢ @Hashnote_Labs' US Yield Coin (USYC)

"We think it's ideal to collectively gather lender liquidity alongside other issuers in Morpho Vaults to drive as much size and efficiency as possible." - @lucasvo, Co-founder of Centrifuge.

This launch represents lots of firsts in the DeFi space:
‚Ä¢ First multi-issuer RWA market
‚Ä¢ First RWA market on Base
‚Ä¢ First application of Coinbase Verifications for this use case

Learn more about how this new market is shaping the future of institutional DeFi and RWAs: https://t.co/MYfSL78FC6

We've recently launched the DeFi Yield Fund (DYF), further closing the gap between TradFi and DeFi.

The DYF is a tokenized fund offering diversified exposure to DeFi yields.

Highlights:
‚Ä¢ Market-neutral strategy for consistent returns
‚Ä¢ Regulated by BVI Financial Services Commission
‚Ä¢ Tokenized shares on multiple networks (Ethereum, Centrifuge Chain, L2s)
‚Ä¢ Strong investor protections and on-chain transparency
‚Ä¢ Diversified portfolio starting with @Re7Capital and Dialectic funds

The DYF's historical performance would have generated:
‚Ä¢ 39.4% in 2021
‚Ä¢ 5.2% in 2022
‚Ä¢ 12.8% in 2023
‚Ä¢ 15.2% YTD 2024

This follows the success of our Liquid Treasury Fund, which has attracted investments from major web3 projects like @fraxfinance, @GnosisDAO, and @Celo.
